{"tid":536031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麗邨欠債男燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-01-21T13:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T11:47:33.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"19fcc52df69f1ef1430f9d0e16abc22fde37a5ae","tid":536031,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"觀塘油麗邨雍麗樓，下午近5時，一名男子被發於屋內燒炭昏迷，救護員到場檢驗證實他已氣絕身亡。警方經初步調查，懷疑事主因欠債問題尋死。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者事前曾將遺書、彩票、單據及現金等入信封寄給家人，惟寫錯地址。收信人今早將信件交給警方才揭發事件。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線：63836568  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180121/57735920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F57735920&d=Pkv6XM7ghmIAJTpJxxntuC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4818bc4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F57735920&h=7c777630\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180121/57735920</a>"},{"pid":"d49b9cbe1ac4f2bf64f7f9894f53559b59a752c8","tid":536031,"uid":29093,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"惟寫錯地址 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdff84dae6a7d7e47f32ab38fc015677781c4901","tid":536031,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"B gor 又害4人😑😑😑"},{"pid":"14978f7905e7deac0